              "free_text": [
                " Preliminary results from the measurement",
                "in 3HUNII - Fig.6 lower of J,EPJ/CS,8,03005 - U-235",
                "normalized, energy-calibrated and background-subtracted",
                "spectra for the 3in.x3in. LaCl3:Ce detector from both",
                "inelastic scattering of fast neutrons and prompt decay",
                "of fission products together with the result of",
                "simulations - counts/(0.98 ns), E from about 0.5 MeV",
                "to 10 MeV; cold neutron beam of the IKI Research",
                "Reactor, lanthanum halide detectors in conjunction",
                "with pCVD diamond detectors."
